{"type":"message","id":"f2a908ce","parentId":"52106709","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:21:25.266Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-14 14:21:23 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52e980eb6d10c2cb0bb599c77b1]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52e980eb6d10c2cb0bb599c77b1\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-14 14:21 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n内容了吗？收到，我刚才发的内容了吗？"}],"timestamp":1776147685265}}
{"type":"message","id":"921510e7","parentId":"f2a908ce","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:22:08.239Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I received their previous messages about the EchoTik new product ranking and product scouting SOP. They sent two messages - the first about the overall approach and the second asking if I received the content.\n\nI did receive and process both messages. I read the skill files for EchoTik. Let me respond confirming I received their message and provide my analysis.\n\nThe user wants to:\n1. Use EchoTik new product ranking as the data source\n2. Filter for products that are:\n   - Listed within the last 3 months (or \"new products\")\n   - Sales volume between 100-300 (some say ≤300, some say just >100)\n   - Showing rising trend (sales trending up)\n   - These are products that are about to blow up\n\nThe goal is to scout these early-stage trending products and get them listed before they become massive hits.\n\nLet me give them a structured response on how to implement this."},{"type":"text","text":"收到了，你说的是**EchoTik 新品榜 + 趋势品跟品**这套打法。让我来梳理一下怎么实现。\n\n---\n\n## 核心筛选逻辑\n\n根据你说的行业经验，趋势品信号是：\n\n| 指标 | 阈值 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 上架时间 | ≤ 90天 | 三个月以内的新品 |\n| 30天销量 | 100 ~ 300单 | 刚好要起量的阶段 |\n| 销量趋势 | 上升（flag=1）| 证明有自然动销 |\n| 评分 | ≥ 4.5 | 质量已经过验证 |\n| 竞争度 | 暂时不设 | 先抓到再说 |\n\n**本质上就是抓\"起爆前夜\"的品**——已经有销量验证，但还没卷成红海。\n\n---\n\n## 技术实现路径\n\n### 第一步：Query EchoTik 新品榜（TH/VN）\n\n用 `listNewProductRank` 接口，参数：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"date\": \"2026-04-14\",\n  \"region\": \"TH\",\n  \"pageNum\": 1,\n  \"pageSize\": 50\n}\n```\n\n拉回来之后，在 Agent 侧做**二次过滤**：\n\n```\n✅ totalSale30dCnt ∈ [100, 300]\n✅ salesTrendFlagText = \"1\" (上升)\n✅ availableDate ≥ 90天前\n✅ 商品类目 = 发饰相关\n✅ IP风险过滤\n```\n\n### 第二步：结合关键词搜索（精筛发饰）\n\n新品榜覆盖面广但不一定精准。**加一层关键词搜索**抓发饰：\n\n用 `listProduct` 接口搜发饰品类（泰语/越南语关键词），筛选刚起量的品：\n\n```\n关键词：\"hair clip\", \"ตัวหนีบผม\" (泰语发夹)\n       \"đồ trang sức tóc\" (越南语发饰)\n30天销量: 100-300\n上架时间: ≤90天\n排序: 30天销量 降序\n```\n\n### 第三步：1688 同款匹配（人工 + 插件）\n\n拿到候选品之后，需要在 1688 上找同款货源。\n\n这一段目前**没有全自动方案**，因为：\n- 1688 没有官方 API 开放给跨境选品\n- 图搜准确率不够高\n- 需要人工判断\"是不是同款\"\n\n建议：**图片 + 标题关键词双重匹配**，把 1688 链接人工填回 Bitable。\n\n### 第四步：图片 + 上架（那个飞书 SOP 的后半段）\n\n这部分就是你说的\"飞书表格 + 店小秘\"的后半段。一旦 1688 链接确定，后面的主图/SKU图生成、利润计算、导出上架，可以全自动跑。\n\n---\n\n## 我建议的 SOP 流程\n\n```\n每日 9:00\n  ↓\nEchoTik 新品榜（TH/VN）→ 拉 50-100 个新品\n  ↓ Agent 过滤\n30天销量 100-300 + 趋势上升 + 发饰类目\n  ↓\nBitable 新品池（采集状态=待审核）\n  ↓ 人工\n确认 1688 同款链接 + 拿样/采购\n  ↓\nBitable 自动化\n  → 抓取 1688 卖点\n  → 标题优化（TikTok 风格）\n  → 主图/SKU 图生成\n  → 利润计算\n  → 导出店小秘上架\n```\n\n---\n\n## 现在卡点\n\n**最大的卡点是 1688 同款匹配**，这一段没有稳定的 API，只能靠人工或者图搜插件。你那边有在用 1688 图搜或者店小秘的插件吗？如果有，可以把它接到 Bitable 的自动化流程里。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776147685267,"responseId":"062d0fe70f71c99eec33c405b47cf3c5"}}
