{"type":"message","id":"ca0fad8e","parentId":"da507547","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:30:00.673Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/3adac96d-4648-4b1f-878c-44dd38c09550.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/3adac96d-4648-4b1f-878c-44dd38c09550.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths - they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 14:29:38 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52e9a3ce9cb8c240f37d221fb56, post, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52e9a3ce9cb8c240f37d221fb56\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-14 14:29 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n[Image]\nUser text:\n[Feishu ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 Tue 2026-04-14 14:29 GMT+8] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 好，那我们现在就一点一点的，我们先把这个路径搞清楚，好吧\n/home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/3adac96d-4648-4b1f-878c-44dd38c09550.jpg\nDescription:\nThis is a screenshot of the EchoTik dashboard, a Chinese e-commerce data analytics platform. The image shows the \"Product Selection Library\" (选品库) interface. It includes robust filtering tools for product categories (like Fashion Accessories), price, and shop types. Currently, filters for the last 7 days' sales are active. At the bottom, a \"Product List\" section displays data columns for GMV and total sales, helping users identify trending products."}],"timestamp":1776148200671}}
{"type":"message","id":"e5c8206a","parentId":"ca0fad8e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:30:26.462Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent a screenshot of the EchoTik dashboard showing a product selection library with filters for categories (Fashion Accessories), price, and shop types, with 7-day sales filters active. The user wants to go step by step to clarify the workflow path.\n\nThis is the EchoTik product selection library interface - this is different from the \"新品榜\" (new product ranking) that we were discussing. This is a more comprehensive product database where you can filter by category, sales, etc.\n\nLet me acknowledge the image and note what I see, then continue the conversation about building out the workflow step by step."},{"type":"text","text":"看到了，这是 EchoTik 的**选品库**页面，不是新品榜——两个入口都在。\n\n从截图里能看到几个关键筛选维度：\n\n- **类目**：时尚配件（Fashion Accessories）—— 我们的发饰品类\n- **时间范围**：7天销量 / 30天销量 / 累计 等\n- **GMV** 和 **总销量** 排序\n- **店铺类型**：精选 / 官方 / 普通\n\n这其实比我们之前聊的新品榜更适合做**趋势品跟品**，因为：\n\n| 对比 | 新品榜 | 选品库（截图这个）|\n|---|---|---|\n| 数据范围 | 纯新品（≤90天）| 全量有销量的品 |\n| 适合场景 | 抓起爆新品 | 找竞争度低的有动销品 |\n| 时间筛选 | 固定新品时间窗口 | 灵活（7天/30天/累计）|\n\n---\n\n**选品库的典型跟品路径：**\n\n```\n7天销量 100-300单  ← 近期有自然动销\n+ 30天销量 100-500单  ← 不要选太爆的（竞争太大）\n+ 店铺类型：精选  ← 质量有背书\n+ 类目：时尚配件  ← 发饰精准\n+ 价格区间：偏低  ← 新手友好\n↓ \n拉出来 → 算利润 → 1688找同款 → 成交\n```\n\n---\n\n好，那我们继续**一点一点来**。\n\n**下一步：确认第一个技术动作——你想先从哪个入口开始拉数据？**\n\n1. **选品库**（截图这个）—— 按筛选条件拉发饰相关品\n2. **新品榜** —— 专门抓三个月内新上架的起爆品\n3. **两个都跑，对比看哪个命中率更高**\n\n你倾向哪个？确认了我们就开始写第一个自动化脚本。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776148200673,"responseId":"062d11ec4ebac1a7e3d311f7b9a26d8f"}}
