{"type":"message","id":"83c702e8","parentId":"5d57b4ec","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:30:29.865Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-14 14:30:27 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52e9a0e9dca8c34ce6786c97e11]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52e9a0e9dca8c34ce6786c97e11\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-14 14:29 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n这个是数据网站，那我们进来之后呢，是直接在新进榜上去找吗？还是这几个榜单我们都要考虑呢？"}],"timestamp":1776148229863}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a4d3369","parentId":"83c702e8","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:30:36.083Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether they should focus on the \"新品榜\" (new product ranking) or consider all the different rankings available on EchoTik. Let me think about what EchoTik rankings typically offer and which ones are most relevant for their use case (finding hair accessories in Thailand and Vietnam with good profit margins).\n\nLet me look at what scripts are available for the echotik skill to understand what data we can pull."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_16r0at2weoa1_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-selector/skills/linkfox-echotik-product-search/scripts/echotik_list_product.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776148229865,"responseId":"062d12061b997378c5c09314a650e333"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a12097a","parentId":"0a4d3369","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:30:36.091Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_16r0at2weoa1_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nEchoTik TikTok Product Search - LinkFox Skill\nCalls the echotik/listProduct API endpoint\n\nUsage:\n  python echotik_list_product.py '{\"keyword\": \"phone case\", \"region\": \"US\", \"minTotalSale30dCnt\": 1000}'\n\"\"\"\n\nimport json\nimport os\nimport sys\nfrom urllib.request import urlopen, Request\nfrom urllib.error import HTTPError, URLError\n\n\nAPI_URL = \"https://tool-gateway.linkfox.com/echotik/listProduct\"\n\n\ndef get_api_key():\n    \"\"\"Retrieve the API key from environment, with a friendly prompt if missing.\"\"\"\n    key = os.environ.get(\"LINKFOXAGENT_API_KEY\")\n    if not key:\n        print(\n            \"API Key not configured. Please complete authorization first:\\n\"\n            \"1. Visit https://yxgb3sicy7.feishu.cn/wiki/GIkkweGghiyzkqkRXQKc2n0Tnre to obtain your Key\\n\"\n            \"2. Set the environment variable: export LINKFOXAGENT_API_KEY=your-key-here\",\n            file=sys.stderr,\n        )\n        sys.exit(1)\n    return key\n\n\ndef call_api(params: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"Call the tool gateway API.\"\"\"\n    api_key = get_api_key()\n    data = json.dumps(params).encode(\"utf-8\")\n\n    req = Request(\n        API_URL,\n        data=data,\n        headers={\n            \"Authorization\": api_key,\n            \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\",\n            \"User-Agent\": \"LinkFox-Skill/1.0\",\n        },\n        method=\"POST\",\n    )\n\n    try:\n        with urlopen(req, timeout=60) as response:\n            return json.loads(response.read().decode(\"utf-8\"))\n    except HTTPError as e:\n        body = e.read().decode(\"utf-8\") if e.fp else \"\"\n        return {\"error\": f\"HTTP {e.code}: {e.reason}\", \"details\": body}\n    except URLError as e:\n        return {\"error\": f\"Connection failed: {e.reason}\"}\n\n\ndef main():\n    if len(sys.argv) < 2:\n        print(\"Usage: echotik_list_product.py '<JSON parameters>'\", file=sys.stderr)\n        print(\n            'Example: echotik_list_product.py \\'{\"keyword\": \"phone case\", \"region\": \"US\", \"minTotalSale30dCnt\": 1000}\\'',\n            file=sys.stderr,\n        )\n        sys.exit(1)\n\n    try:\n        params = json.loads(sys.argv[1])\n    except json.JSONDecodeError as e:\n        print(f\"Invalid parameter format: {e}\", file=sys.stderr)\n        sys.exit(1)\n\n    result = call_api(params)\n    print(json.dumps(result, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776148236089}}
{"type":"message","id":"bfd428df","parentId":"0a12097a","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:31:04.242Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the EchoTik tools better. There are two main data entry points:\n\n1. **listNewProductRank** - 新品榜 (New Product Ranking) - what I already documented\n2. **listProduct** - 选品库/商品搜索 (Product Search/Selection Library) - what the screenshot shows\n\nThe user is asking whether they should focus on the 新品榜 (new product ranking) or consider multiple ranking sources.\n\nLooking at the available tools:\n- `listNewProductRank`: For new products (fresh on the platform)\n- `listProduct`: For general product search with rich filters\n\nFor the user's use case (finding hair accessories in TH/VN with 100-300 monthly sales), let me think about which approach is better:\n\n\nThe 新品榜 is too narrow since it's filtered to products listed within 90 days, which might miss established items with steady sales. The 选品库 is more flexible—I can apply custom filters like the 7-day sales range and sort by total volume to surface products that are genuinely popular and potentially less saturated.\n\nGiven the user's stated goal of finding items with sales between 100-300, I should be pulling from both sources: use 新品榜 to catch early signals on trending products before they blow up, then cross-reference those findings with 选品库 data filtered to the same sales threshold to validate they're worth pursuing."},{"type":"text","text":"这两个入口其实**面向不同目的**，建议分开用、都跑，但优先级不同：\n\n---\n\n## 三个榜单的用途\n\n| 榜单 | 适合找什么 | 我们的优先级 |\n|------|-----------|------------|\n| **新品榜** | 抓起爆苗子（≤90天新上架）| 🔴 重点，命中率最高 |\n| **爆品榜** | 找已经爆了的品 | ⚪ 参考，竞争太卷 |\n| **飙升榜** | 找突然爆发的品 | 🟡 辅助，快速跟品 |\n\n**你选的那个\"7天销量100-300\"的逻辑，其实最适合用新品榜**——刚上架不久就有动销，证明市场已经在帮我们验证了。\n\n---\n\n## 建议的执行策略\n\n**第一步（每天必跑）：新品榜**\n- 拉 TH + VN 两个站\n- 筛选：7天销量 50-500 + 上升趋势（抓最早期信号）\n- 这个是跟品成功率最高的入口\n\n**第二步（每天跑一次）：选品库**\n- 按截图那样设筛选条件\n- 7天销量 / 30天销量 双向验证\n- 找\"老品里的遗珠\"——有稳定动销但竞争还不大的\n\n**第三步（每周跑一次）：飙升榜**\n- 看最近哪类发饰在突然起量\n- 做选品方向的趋势判断\n\n---\n\n好，明确了。我们现在的第一步就是：\n\n> **从 EchoTik 新品榜（TH + VN）拉数据，筛选 7天销量 50-500 + 上升趋势 + 发饰类目**\n\n确认这个方向的话，我现在就可以帮你调接口跑第一波数据出来，你看看命中率如何？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776148236092,"responseId":"062d120c0aa5363853a74fd77f33de66"}}
