{"type":"message","id":"445b546f","parentId":"d0c8bcf5","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:39:07.482Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-14 14:39:05 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52ea5e4f6808c2148b35c04d65e]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52ea5e4f6808c2148b35c04d65e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-14 14:39 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n步骤一，进入https://echotik.live/，右上方 进入当前区域，如越南。进入新品榜，时尚配件类目--发饰类目，也可以进入三级类目 发绳，发带发箍，发夹发簪。等子类目。"}],"timestamp":1776148747480}}
{"type":"message","id":"168ddaaa","parentId":"445b546f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:39:29.159Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is giving me specific step-by-step instructions on how to navigate EchoTik to access the new product rankings for Vietnam (VN) market, specifically in the fashion accessories > hair accessories category, with subcategories like hair ties, headbands, hair clips, hair sticks etc.\n\nThis is a manual process they're describing - going to echotik.live, selecting Vietnam region, then going to New Product Ranking, then selecting the fashion accessories category, then hair accessories subcategory, and further into sub-subcategories like hair ties, headbands, hair clips, hair sticks.\n\nLet me acknowledge this and confirm I understand the navigation path. I should also note that we're building toward an automated process, but understanding the manual steps first helps define what we need to automate.\n\n\nNow I need to reflect back what I've understood from their instructions to confirm I'm on the right track, and ask what specific data or information they're looking to extract or accomplish through this navigation."},{"type":"text","text":"明白，这是手动操作的完整路径。让我整理一下：\n\n---\n\n## EchoTik 越南站新品榜 - 完整导航路径\n\n```\n1. 进入 https://echotik.live/\n2. 右上角 → 切换区域到「越南」(VN)\n3. 点击「新品榜」\n4. 选择类目路径：\n   时尚配件 → 发饰类目\n   ├── 发绳\n   ├── 发带/发箍\n   ├── 发夹/发簪\n   └── （其他子类目）\n```\n\n泰国站同理，切换到 TH 即可。\n\n---\n\n## 这是在帮我们确认\"手工选品的完整动作链\"\n\n你现在一步步带我过这个流程，其实是在帮我理解：\n\n1. **手动跑一遍** → 知道每步操作什么、数据长什么样\n2. **自动化拆解** → 哪些步骤可以 API 替代，哪些必须人工\n\n---\n\n## 确认下一步\n\n目前看：\n- 类目选择（发饰 → 子类目）→ **可 API 参数化**（categoryKeywordCN）\n- 区域切换（VN/TH）→ **API 参数化**（region）\n- 日期选择 → **API 参数化**（date）\n\n**目前卡点还是：1688 同款匹配 + 利润率自动计算**，这两步没有标准化 API。\n\n---\n\n继续，你在页面上看到的数据长什么样——能看到 7天销量、30天销量、达人数量、佣金率这些指标吗？如果能看到，我现在就可以帮你设计第一版筛选参数。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776148747482,"responseId":"062d140c59348584ec08ae8778f4fc01"}}
