{"type":"message","id":"c355c8c0","parentId":"fce56a2b","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:40:12.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is showing me another EchoTik screenshot of the \"Product Leaderboard\" (商品排行榜) for \"New Products\" (新品榜). I can see:\n\n- Filters: Release date 2026-04-07, category 时尚配件 (Fashion Accessories)\n- A data table with ranked products showing:\n  - Product name & image (mixed Chinese and Vietnamese)\n  - A badge showing \"3.7\" (likely rating or some metric)\n  - Total sales volume\n  - 7-day sales\n  - Number of active sellers or similar metric\n  - Whether it's an officially certified store or not\n  - Revenue metrics\n\nI need to analyze what fields are visible and understand what data points we can extract from this view, so I can map them to our SOP's required fields.\n\nLet me look at the image to identify all visible data fields so I can help the user understand what's available from the API versus what they see on screen.\n\n\nLooking at the table columns, I'm trying to map out what each visible field represents—whether it's total sales, 7-day sales volume, seller count, or store certification status. The API should return all these metrics including product titles, prices, various sales windows, GMV figures, trend indicators, engagement metrics like videos and live streams, commission rates, ratings, review counts, and availability dates.\n\nThe category filter \"时尚配件\" is already showing on the left sidebar, and it looks like they have subcategories like \"发饰\" expanded. I should clarify which specific subcategories they want to pull from since they're selecting different product types. I need to understand what specific subcategories fall under 发饰 so I can map them to the correct filter values in the API call, rather than trying to guess the category structure."},{"type":"text","text":"好，这个数据表格的字段很清晰了。我来拆解一下：\n\n---\n\n## 截图里能看到的数据字段\n\n| # | 字段名（截图列）| 说明 | API 能否获取 |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | 商品图片 + 标题 | 商品基础信息 | ✅ imageUrl + title |\n| 2 | 评分/勋章 | 3.7 可能是某种质量分 | ❓ 待确认 |\n| 3 | **总销量** | 累计销量 | ✅ totalSaleCnt |\n| 4 | **7天销量** | 近7天销量 | ✅ totalSale7dCnt（如果有） |\n| 5 | **在售商品数** | 有多少店在卖这款 | ❓ 可能需确认 |\n| 6 | **是否官方认证** | 精选/官方标识 | ✅ 店铺类型 |\n| 7 | **30天销量** | 近30天销量 | ✅ totalSale30dCnt |\n| 8 | **30天销售额** | GMV | ✅ totalSaleGmv30dAmt |\n\n---\n\n## 从截图能读到的关键信息\n\n- **日期筛选**：2026-04-07（最近7天）\n- **类目**：时尚配件 → 可以展开到发饰子类目\n- **越南站点**：✅ 确认是 VN\n- **有官方认证标识**：说明是精选品\n\n---\n\n## 我看到左侧有类目树\n\n截图左侧能看到**发饰**的子类目展开。你现在勾选的是哪几个子类目？\n\n- 发绳\n- 发带/发箍\n- 发夹/发簪\n- 其他？\n\n确认后我帮你设计第一版 API 筛选参数，直接用 EchoTik 的关键词搜索接口（`listProduct`）把类目 + 销量条件 + 区域 + 日期条件组合起来跑。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776148785376,"responseId":"062d14319fa8b0309cd06714a268378f"}}
